    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚和索马里同意合作打击叛乱分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/ethiopia-somalia-agree-to-collaborate-on-countering-insurgents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚和索马里同意共同组建一支多国部队来打击伊斯兰叛乱分子，这意味着这两个邻国之间的外交紧张局势将进一步缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/ethiopia-somalia-agree-to-collaborate-on-countering-insurgents</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:48:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚王宫称所有赦免请求必须经过国王批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/malaysia-palace-says-all-pardon-bids-must-come-through-king</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据马来西亚王宫发表的声明称，对在马来西亚联邦直辖区犯下的罪行的赦免请求必须提交给由国王苏丹易卜拉欣·伊斯坎达尔主持的赦免委员会，正如被监禁的前总理纳吉布拉扎克正在通过法院寻求软禁一样。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/malaysia-palace-says-all-pardon-bids-must-come-through-king</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷考虑向投资基金或国际货币基金组织申请新贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/argentina-weighing-new-loans-from-either-investment-funds-or-imf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员称，阿根廷政府正在评估是否与两家投资基金协商贷款或向国际货币基金组织寻求额外融资，以便为未来几个月取消货币和资本管制铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/argentina-weighing-new-loans-from-either-investment-funds-or-imf</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将于周五阻止新日铁收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/biden-to-block-planned-us-steel-takeover-washington-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，美国总统乔·拜登已决定阻止将美国钢铁公司出售给日本新日铁公司，从而结束一项价值 141 亿美元的交易。该交易数月来一直遭到强烈反对，并引发了人们对这家美国工业巨头未来的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/biden-to-block-planned-us-steel-takeover-washington-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据哥伦比亚广播公司报道，拜登最早将于周五宣布美国钢铁决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/biden-to-announce-us-steel-decision-as-early-as-friday-cbs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据哥伦比亚广播公司援引知情人士透露，美国总统拜登将于周五就是否批准新日本制铁公司收购美国钢铁公司做出决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/biden-to-announce-us-steel-decision-as-early-as-friday-cbs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:50:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在削减税收前任命肯·凯斯担任财政部关键税收政策职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-picks-ken-kies-for-key-tax-policy-job-at-treasury-ahead-of-cuts-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布了财政部高级领导团队成员，他们将与他挑选的财政部长斯科特·贝森特一起工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/trump-picks-ken-kies-for-key-tax-policy-job-at-treasury-ahead-of-cuts-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 01:04:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
